responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B43289F0459B988EDFFC57B235C2A1D2", "Then we are in a secret alliance. I cannot promise my blades will not harm you. They see only their fellow bandits as allies. Such is a secret alliance. And as part of that union, mine all you want, but I expect something special in return, something ancient and rare. Should you excavate or hear whispers of any minotaur artifacts etched with the symbol of two spears and a crown, I want it! Do not disappoint me. ")
